title: "Quantiles: Local-first AI evaluation infrastructure"

abstract: >-
  Quantiles is agent-native, local-first infrastructure for running AI evaluations and benchmarks, inspecting sample-level outputs, and comparing evaluation runs through its CLI and SDKs.

